window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Ye screw with this lass, ye get put on yer ass.</p> <p>It is the Time of the Colliding Realms—the Keening—the Culling.</p> <p>Everything that happened over the past eighteen months has led to this moment. The good and the bad. The triumphs and the tragedies. Now my family by blood, by choice, and by circumstance face the battle to balance our world's alignment.</p> <p>United as Team Light.</p> <p>When rays of first morn's light warm the depths of the sacred tomb / The powers of dark and light will hold their ground or seal their doom. Yeah, that's not daunting at all.</p> <p>Attacked by powerful players from all sides, enemies, allies, and a few surprise guests rally to fight the fight of the millennium. Even if we win this war, the world as we know it will never be the same.</p> <p>Fiona brings you more druid adventure, family shenanigans, and mythical tales of magic and mystery in A Danger Destroyed, the fifteenth and final installment of the Chronicles of an Urban Druid.</p>"; 
